.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-CAPACITY-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-capacity-max \- FEAT-2453 peer with highest total channel capacity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-capacity-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the peer with the highest total channel capacity (local_msat + remote_msat) for lightning CLI (FEAT-2453).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
